Server.NetworkInterface.Communication

Class FakeCommunication

  • java.lang.Object
    • Server.NetworkInterface.Communication.BaseCommunication
      • Server.NetworkInterface.Communication.FakeCommunication

  • public class FakeCommunication
extends BaseCommunication
    It is the way in which it is connected FakeUser. In this case we can override any method of leaving the actions within this fake user meaningless. Created by Giulio on 16/06/2016.
